    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only post office in a small village in the mountains, the main character of this story, Brass, works here. His job is to deliver letters and packages to the local people. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Brass receives a letter from his grandmother who lives in a town by the sea, and a new adventure begins. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Peaceful, Cozy Adventure Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story progresses through conversations with the villagers and errands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no combat or intense action in this game. Please enjoy it in a relaxed atmosphere. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002060/extras/575ce0d2ee85cc5ce1c46ccaa344d27c.avif?t=1768648012\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Little Mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, there are a few mysteries that call forth more mysteries. (Exaggerated?)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What is the secret behind his father's death? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cursed forest?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A secret underground facility?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Calm Background Music</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features music by four composers: Tomás Palazzi, Svyatoslav Petrov, Josh Kashdan and Kyle Booth. All of the music was written exclusively for this game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please play the demo version and listen to the music for yourself. All of the tracks are gentle and wonderful, and you'll want to listen to them over and over again. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Characters and Animals</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character, Brass, is a 14-year-old boy who has started working at the post office to help support his family. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002060/extras/41e207f6ec0bb5ac4abfc168d82da99d.poster.avif?t=1768648012\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002060/extras/41e207f6ec0bb5ac4abfc168d82da99d.webm?t=1768648012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002060/extras/41e207f6ec0bb5ac4abfc168d82da99d.mp4?t=1768648012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll also meet many other characters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002060/extras/63d322e09c94041fd42637703fbafbb9.avif?t=1768648012\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002060/extras_big/63d322e09c94041fd42637703fbafbb9.avif?t=1768648012 width=800 height=466 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scenery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story takes place in a mountain village and a seaside town. Brass runs around in the cute isometric-ish sceneries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002060/extras/9db5d12385d3dbbe7a0a66fc96fa33e4.avif?t=1768648012\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002060/extras_big/9db5d12385d3dbbe7a0a66fc96fa33e4.avif?t=1768648012 width=800 height=677 /></span></p>",
